To clarify someone on here said all gays who are straight passing do this which just isn't true before anyone gets all butt hurt. It's horrible for people to be bullied but to turn around and bully in return is just dumb.

And in this case what we're talking about is hypothetical, of course it can be applied to real life situations such as someone actually bullying another for being gay because they themselves don't accept that they are gay and hold a lot of internal self hatred and anger, which is sadly an all to real thing in the community. In this case both parties are victims of homophobia. 

So don't be a dumbass who says this is something all "straight passing gays do" you sound like an idiot. 

And for people who were on either end of this I hope you both love yourself whether you're effeminate or not.
